#Cordova iOS Xcode Plugin Templates ###Installation: ###`$ git clone https://github.com/RandyMcMillan/cdv-ios-plugin-templates.git` ###`$ ./installer install` ###Commands: ###`$ ./installer install` - Recursively initializes submodules (so you don't need to worry about it)!

###`$ ./installer uninstall` - This removes symlinks

###`$ ./installer upgrade` - pulls from repos and reinitializes submodules.

###`$ ./installer help` - List of commands in terminal .

###`$ ./installer readme` - Open http://randymcmillan.github.com/cdv-ios-plugin-templates/ in browser.
name: CDV-iOS-Plugin-Templates
